***********
1. Overview
***********

This directory contains the source files for the buffer bomb. Don't
use the Makefile in this directory to build your bombs. Use the
./makebomb program instead.

********
2. Files
********

config.h: Contains list of hosts where this lab may be run

driverlib.{h,c}: 
	Contains common driver support functions.

bufbomb.c (bufbomb):  
	A bomb program that is solved using a buffer overflow attack.

hex2raw.c (hex2raw): 
	Converts a text string into raw bytes and emits it on stdout.

makecookie.c and gencookie.c (makecookie):
	Generates and emits the cookie associated with a userid.

support.{c,h}
	Contains helper functions.

